subsection.leadIn:
The Registrar must not disclose any withheld information to a public officer or
                public body if the officer or body fails to provide the Registrar with a statement,
                made by the officer or body, confirming that—

The Registrar must not disclose any withheld information to a scheduled person
                if the person fails to provide the Registrar with a statement, made by the person,
                confirming that—
